From 0fd6b30e6181e10fcc30a1e23618e97adc9f3441 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
Date: Thu, 26 Feb 2026 23:45:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 01/26] treewide: fix uImage.FIT document paths

Commit 488445cefa1 ("doc: Move FIT into its own directory") moved the
documentation in doc/uImage.FIT to doc/usage/fit, subsequently all
documents and example sources have been converted to reStructuredText.

Fix (almost) all of the remaining occurances of the old path and
filenames accross the tree.

Signed-off-by: Daniel Golle <daniel@makrotopia.org>
---
 README                                             | 2 +-
 board/technexion/pico-imx7d/README.pico-imx7d_BL33 | 2 +-
